# Dashboard (Phase A)

## Folders

- Unlimited depth tree (Adjacency List model when BE connected)
- DnD move folder/material
- Recent folders strip (last 10 visited)
- Upload only to leaf folders (folders with children block upload)

## Sort (3 options)

| Value | Label | Logic |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `recent` | 최근 열람순 | `lastStudiedAt` desc, nulls last |
| `created` | 생성일순 | `uploadedAt` desc |
| `folder` | 폴더순 | folder name, then date |

`lastStudiedAt` updated when study workspace opens (`StudyShell` mount).

## Upload (Phase A)

- Formats: PDF, JPG, PNG
- Max size: 50MB
- PDF max pages: 100 (TRD)
- Images: single-page viewer (OCR Phase C)

## Search

- Filename only (Phase A); full-text search is Phase B

## Key files

- `LibraryToolbar.tsx`, `useDashboardLibrary.ts`
- `FileUploadDialog.tsx` (was PdfUploadDialog)
- `src/lib/mocks/materials.ts`, `src/constants/upload.ts`
